# Pre-commit pattern list (EXAMPLE — commit this; do NOT put real patterns here).
#
# Copy this file to `.githooks/patterns.local` (gitignored) and add one
# extended-regex pattern per line. Lines starting with # and blank lines
# are ignored. Patterns are matched case-insensitively against added lines
# in staged diffs.
#
# The pre-commit hook reads ONLY `.githooks/patterns.local`. If it does
# not exist, no content scanning is performed.

# Example format (replace with your organisation's sensitive patterns):
# internal\.example\.com
# corp-staging\.example\.net
# AKIA[0-9A-Z]{16}
